### User/Device

![configuration-2.png](/plex/configuration-2.png)

1. Table of all users and devices. Uncheck the notify box to not receive notifications from the specific user/device.
1. Keyword for having the bot display what is currently streaming on your server.

### Session Killing

![configuration-3.png](/plex/configuration-3.png)

1. Kill all sessions from a given user/device (Maybe a user shared their login with someone else)
1. Kill the session after rules have been met
1. Notify when sessions are automatically killed

### Library Trash

![configuration-4.png](/plex/configuration-4.png)

1. Keyword to trigger a cleanup outside the set frequency and time
2. Check which libraries you want the automated trash cleanup
3. The time and frequency of the automated cleanup
4. The times for the library

